'''Sirpar Station''' was a transfer station located at the entrance to the [[Sirpar Hills]] and [[Pols Anaxes]], on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Anaxes/Legends|Anaxes]]. It was here that the [[Anaxsi]] exchanged their [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeders]] and groundcars for [[Keffi/Legends|Keffis]]. This was due to most vehicles being banned in both the Hills and the Capital.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

